===============================================================================

CHANGELOG:

v0.3:
- add announcement befor the countdown starts
- add compatibility with Permissions

v0.2:
- change /fight to /fight <seconds>

v0.1:
- add /fight to count from 5 to 1


===============================================================================

DEPENDENCIES:

- Bukkit (http://www.bukkit.org) - A SMP plugin API
- Permissions (http://forums.bukkit.org/threads/5974/)
		- An permission system for Bukkit


===============================================================================

COMMANDS:

/fight <seconds> - set up a countdown.
	fightcountdown.fight (to allow the command in Permissions)